    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1961-01-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1961-01-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="230"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d230">
                <head>230. Record of Action, January 19<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d230fn1">
                        <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Action No. 2395: Attack warning
                        channels and procedures for civilians. Secret. 1 p. Department of State,
                            <gloss target="#t_SS_1">S/S</gloss>–<gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>
                        (Miscellaneous) Files: Lot 66 D 95, Records of Action by the National
                        Security Council.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1961-01-19">January 19, 1961</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d230-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d230-1"/>
                <p>The Assistant Secretary of the Treasury, the Attorney General, the Director,
                    Bureau of the Budget, and the Chairman, Atomic Energy Commission, participated
                    in the action below.</p>
                <table cols="2" rows="2">
                    <row>
                        <cell>ACTION NUMBER</cell>
                        <cell>SUBJECT</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell role="num">2395.</cell>
                        <cell>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="italic">ATTACK WARNING CHANNELS AND PROCEDURES FOR
                                    CIVILIANS</hi>
                            </p>
                            <p>(<gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> 5513/1; <gloss
                                    target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Action No. 1565; Memos for <gloss
                                    target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>, same subject, dated February 20,
                                1957, December 3, 1959, and December 14 and 28, 1960; <gloss
                                    target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Action No. 2363; Memo for <gloss
                                    target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> from Executive Secretary, same
                                subject, dated January 17, 1961)</p>
                            <p>Adopted the chart on the subject transmitted by the reference
                                memorandum of January 17, 1961.</p>
                            <p>NOTE: The above action, as approved by the President, subsequently
                                transmitted to all holders of <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>
                                5513/1.</p>
                        </cell>
                    </row>
                </table>
            </div>
        </body>
